# GIS Toolbox — legacy agent rules (see .cursor/rules/ and AGENTS.md)

GIT WORKFLOW (MANDATORY):
- Develop locally on staging only. Never edit main during feature work.
- Only two branches: main (production) and staging (development). No feature branches.
- Do not commit, push, merge, or create PRs unless the user explicitly asks.
- User commits and merges via GitHub Desktop.
- Read AGENTS.md and docs/DEVELOPMENT.md for full details.

GIS WIDGETS (new or changed panel wizards):
- Read docs/WIDGET_AGENT_PLAYBOOK.md first, then docs/WIDGET_AUTHORING.md.
- Register in js/widgets/registry.js; wire via js/widgets/<id>/controller.js.
